            <thetext>We need a way to check whether an effect is already running.
Therefore we would like to have a method like qx.fx.Base.isRunning().

The class qx.fx.Base already maintains the private variable &quot;__state&quot;, but unfortunately, there is no method that returns this state.

We need this method &quot;isRunning()&quot; because we want to avoid to restart an effect if the effect is still running.</thetext>
